        newsArticle1Subtitle: "Recovery of Corona Emergency Aid: Current Developments",
        newsArticle1Intro: "Many Hessian entrepreneurs have recently received mail from the Kassel Regional Council. Five years after the Corona pandemic, the state is demanding a so-called \"feedback\" on the Corona emergency aid paid out at the time. In the worst case, there is a threat of recovery of the emergency aid.",
        newsArticle1Section1Title: "Why recoveries now?",
        newsArticle1Section1Text1: "The Corona emergency aid from spring 2020 was intended to protect companies from economic hardship in an unbureaucratic way. The promise was quick help without lengthy examination procedures. However, the approvals were subject to reservation: Those who could not later prove a real liquidity shortage should repay the Corona aid.",
