        // Entrepreneurs page
        entrepreneursTitle: "Services for Entrepreneurs",
        entrepreneursSubtitle: "Professional tax consulting for your business",
        entrepreneursDigitalTitle: "Digital on the go",
        entrepreneursDigitalDescription1: "The digital age is here – with all its challenges, but also its advantages. We want you to benefit from it too.",
        entrepreneursDigitalDescription2: "Unternehmen online creates individual opportunities for collaboration between you and Heilgendorff Tax Office via the DATEV cloud – both for financial accounting and payroll.",
        entrepreneursDigitalDescription3: "Get involved in your financial accounting! You can access your data at any time and upload documents, bringing you closer to the action than ever before.",
        entrepreneursFeaturesTitle: "These possibilities are offered by Unternehmen online:",
        entrepreneursFeature1: "A system for the complete commercial process as well as for upstream and downstream processes in payroll",
        entrepreneursFeature2: "Original receipts and documents remain in the company – an audit-proof electronic document archive is available at any time",
        entrepreneursFeature3: "Quick access to meaningful and differentiated business and personnel evaluations",
        entrepreneursFeature4: "Maintaining an electronic cash book",
        entrepreneursFeature5: "Saving postage costs",
        entrepreneursFeature6: "Quick exchange and transparency",
        entrepreneursDatevInfo: "Do you have further questions about DATEV Unternehmen Online?",
        entrepreneursDatevHelpTextBefore: "Further information can be found here in the",
        entrepreneursDatevHelpTextAfter: ".",
        entrepreneursDatevHelpLink: "DATEV Help Center",
        entrepreneursDatevTitle1: "Digitalization with",
        entrepreneursDatevTitle2: "DATEV Unternehmen Online",
        entrepreneursDatevDescription: "Get further illustrations and information about DATEV software.",
        entrepreneursDatevButton: "DATEV Unternehmen Online",
        entrepreneursQuote: "\"The payment of taxes cannot be refused for reasons of conscience.\"",
        entrepreneursQuoteAuthor: "BFH ruling of 12/06/1991, BStBl 1992 II page 303",
        entrepreneursServicesTitle: "Our range of services:",
        entrepreneursService1Title: "Digital Accounting",
        entrepreneursService1Description: "Professional accounting with modern digital tools",
        entrepreneursService2Title: "Digital Payroll Accounting",
        entrepreneursService2Description: "Efficient payroll processing",
        entrepreneursService3Title: "Annual Financial Statements or Profit Determination",
        entrepreneursService3Description: "Transparent and clean annual financial statements",
        entrepreneursService4Title: "Startup Consulting",
        entrepreneursService4Description: "Professional support from idea to implementation",
        entrepreneursService5Title: "Support during Tax Audits",
        entrepreneursService5Description: "Competent support during audits",
        entrepreneursService1DetailTitle: "Digital Accounting",
        entrepreneursService1DetailText1: "We have had experience with digital accounting for more than 10 years and have been using DATEV Unternehmen online for 4 years.",
        entrepreneursService1DetailText2: "The tax office requires clean and timely financial management. Using digital solutions, we make accounting as uncomplicated as possible for you too. The magic words here are digital document transfer and electronic retrieval of account statements.",
        entrepreneursService1DetailText3: "You can comfortably capture documents digitally in your company and then transmit them directly to us online. In addition, there is the \"DATEV Upload mobil\" app, with which you can digitally capture receipts, for example, directly with your smartphone while on the go. Documents are recorded upon receipt and no longer need to be sorted laboriously. This brings significant time savings in preparing the accounting!",
        entrepreneursService1DetailText4: "Electronic retrieval of account statements and document transfer enable us to provide timely accounting where you always have your receivables and payables exactly in view.",
        entrepreneursService1DetailSubtitle: "In addition to posting your documents, we offer you the following services:",
        entrepreneursService1DetailItem1: "Monthly recording of depreciation",
        entrepreneursService1DetailItem2: "Monthly recording of all private portions",
        entrepreneursService1DetailItem3: "Recording of imputed costs (imputed rent, imputed entrepreneur salary, imputed depreciation, etc.)",
        entrepreneursService1DetailItem4: "Recording of target values",
        entrepreneursService1DetailItem5: "Cost accounting",
        entrepreneursService1DetailItem6: "Reminder of open items",
        entrepreneursService2DetailTitle: "Digital Payroll Accounting",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText1: "The process for payroll and salary accounting can also be completely digitized with us using Unternehmen Online.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText2: "You can upload all relevant documents, such as employee questionnaires, employee timesheets, vacation days, sick leave certificates, etc., directly into the digital personnel file and no longer need to keep separate lists. Changes to master data and the recording of new employees in the company can also be easily made in Unternehmen Online.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText3: "After data processing, you will receive payroll evaluations immediately digitally in Unternehmen Online and can view them anywhere and at any time.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText4: "Some comfortable automations are also possible. On request, we can make payments for social security contributions and wages/salaries directly from the system. For this, a transfer slip is created for your house bank and submitted to it. After successful accounting, you can release the wage payment and your house bank will then execute it as a bulk transfer. Individual transfers are thus eliminated for you.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText5: "In addition, all transmitted data is stored digitally in the DATEV data center and thus securely archived. If needed, these documents can be quickly reproduced for you and your employees.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText6: "For your employees, there is the \"Arbeitnehmer Online\" module. Through this, your employees can access their own payroll documents online. This saves paper and time.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailText7: "We process hourly wages, fixed salaries and construction wages, submit applications such as A1 certificates and help you determine the optimal net salary.",
        entrepreneursService2DetailSubtitle: "Our range of services includes, among others:",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem1: "Setting up your payroll and salary accounting",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem2: "Creating ongoing payroll and salary statements",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem3: "Recording and managing vacation days",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem4: "Calculating gratuitous value transfers",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem5: "Careful maintenance of personnel master data",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem6: "Maintaining annual payroll journals",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem7: "Conscientious transmission of contribution certificates and payroll tax returns",
        entrepreneursService2DetailItem8: "Applying for continued wage payment in case of illness and maternity benefits",
        entrepreneursService2DetailExpert: "Our payroll expert is available to you at any time.",
        entrepreneursService3DetailTitle: "Annual Financial Statements or Profit Determination",
        entrepreneursService3DetailText1: "After 12 months, a line is drawn under the financial year: A transparent and clean annual financial statement must be created. An annual financial statement is usually of interest to several groups of addressees. The publication of the annual financial statement itself and the manner in which it is done are also dependent on legal form and size. In some cases, only a balance sheet needs to be filed.",
        entrepreneursService3DetailText2: "In addition to the required submission to the tax office and publication with the Federal Office of Justice, the annual financial statement and balance sheet primarily serve as a control element for your business success. Because the annual financial statement and balance sheet provide information about the development of your company in the past and thus also impulses for future business activities and targeted decisions.",
        entrepreneursService3DetailText3: "We look at what requirements are placed on your company. Through our years of experience, we not only create your financial statements but also advise you individually on promising measures for the future.",
        entrepreneursService3DetailSubtitle: "We create for you:",
        entrepreneursService3DetailItem1: "Balance sheets according to HGB and tax balance sheets",
        entrepreneursService3DetailItem2: "A detailed balance sheet report",
        entrepreneursService3DetailItem3: "Profit determination and annual financial statements",
        entrepreneursService3DetailItem4: "Transmissions for the electronic Federal Gazette",
        entrepreneursService4DetailTitle: "Startup",
        entrepreneursService4DetailText1: "Starting a new company requires some important decisions from you as an entrepreneur. We are pleased to be able to offer our many years of expertise in this field as well.",
        entrepreneursService4DetailText2: "In an individual consultation, we discuss with you the essential topics to be considered for your upcoming startup. We will answer all detailed questions that arise during this initial conversation in a further conversation or send them to you uncomplicatedly if you wish.",
        entrepreneursService4DetailSubtitle: "The focus of our consulting is:",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem1: "Feasibility study",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem2: "Consulting on optimal legal form and contracts such as articles of association, etc.",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem3: "Liability risks and tax advance planning",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem4: "Consulting on financing options and support in obtaining financing",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem5: "Applying for funding and startup grants",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem6: "Design of business accounting",
        entrepreneursService4DetailItem7: "Consulting on securing private risks such as illness, disability or death",
        entrepreneursService5DetailTitle: "Tax Audits",
        entrepreneursService5DetailText1: "Of course, we also stand by your side in unpleasant and difficult situations.",
        entrepreneursService5DetailText2: "We support you during tax audits by tax offices, social security institutions and other authorities. From the auditor's registration, through the ongoing audit itself, to the final discussion, we are there as a competent contact person. Afterwards, we review the audit reports and evaluate the results. We ensure a smooth process.",
        entrepreneursService5DetailSubtitle: "We accompany you in these areas:",
        entrepreneursService5DetailItem1: "Tax audit",
        entrepreneursService5DetailItem2: "Payroll tax field audit",
        entrepreneursService5DetailItem3: "VAT special audit and inspection",
