        individualsService1DetailTitle: "Income Tax Return Preparation",
        individualsService1DetailText1: "Preparing income tax returns can be a major challenge for individuals, especially when many different types of income are present. This often leaves many tax opportunities unused.",
        individualsService1DetailText2: "With us, the professional preparation of your income tax return with optimization and savings opportunities is in the foreground. We take time for your individual consultation and accompany you from the submission of your documents to the review of the tax assessment.",
        individualsService1DetailText3: "The submission of documents is increasingly simplified as part of digitization: At Heilgendorff Tax Office, we work with the \"DATEV Meine Steuern\" program, through which you have the opportunity to quickly and easily forward your tax-relevant documents to us. In addition, we naturally still accept the classic submission of documents in paper form.",
        individualsService1DetailSubtitle: "The following services are associated with the preparation of your income tax return:",
